/******************************************/
/* POPULATION EVENT - Suspected Infection */
/******************************************/

/* All Order-Question Responses with an Instance of the Following Words:
    * Infection
    * Infected
    * Infectious
    * Infect
*/

/* Grain: Order-question response */

/* Note: Even though antibiotics are likely to be the only medication orders with a mention of
   "infection," this binding looks at all medication-order-question responses regardless of
   medication type. */

/* Infection-Related Order-Question Responses */
WITH OrderQuestionResponse AS (
SELECT
    peh.HospitalAccountID AS FacilityAccountID
   ,peh.PatientEncounterID
   ,ord.OrderID
   ,ord.OrderStatusDSC
   ,COALESCE(ord.OrderingProviderID,ord.MedicationPrescribingProviderID,ord.AuthorizingProviderID,'Unknown') AS OrderQuestionResponseProviderID
   ,COALESCE(OrdProv.ProviderFullNM,'Unknown') AS OrderQuestionResponseProviderNM
   ,COALESCE(OrdProv.PrimarySpecialtyNM,'Unknown') AS OrderQuestionResponseProviderSpecialtyNM
   ,ord.MedicationID AS OrderQuestionResponseMedicationID
   ,mref.MedicationDSC AS OrderQuestionResponseMedicationNM
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassCD AS OrderQuestionResponseTherapeuticClassCD
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassDSC AS OrderQuestionResponseTherapeuticClassNM
   ,ord.OrderInstantDTS AS OrderQuestionResponseDTS
--   ,q.QuestionTypeDSC AS OrderQuestionTypeDSC
   ,oqr.QuestionID AS OrderQuestionID
--   ,q.QuestionNM AS OrderQuestionNM
   ,oqr.LineNBR AS OrderQuestionResponseLineNBR
   ,oqr.OrderQuestionResponseTXT
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY peh.PatientEncounterID,ord.MedicationID ORDER BY oqr.LineNBR) AS OrderQuestionResponseSequenceNBR
FROM Epic.Encounter.PatientEncounterHospital AS peh
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Medication AS ord
   ON ord.PatientEncounterID = peh.PatientEncounterID
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.QuestionResponse AS oqr
   ON ord.OrderID = oqr.OrderID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Reference.Medication AS mref
   ON ord.MedicationID = mref.MedicationID
--LEFT JOIN Epic.Reference.QuestionnaireQuestion AS q
--   ON q.QuestionID = oqr.QuestionID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Shared.Person.Provider AS OrdProv
   ON COALESCE(ord.OrderingProviderID,ord.MedicationPrescribingProviderID,ord.AuthorizingProviderID) = OrdProv.EDWProviderID
WHERE oqr.OrderQuestionResponseTXT LIKE '% infect%' /* Only order-question responses with "infection," "infected," "infectious," "infect." */
)

SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,OrderID
   ,OrderStatusDSC
   ,OrderQuestionResponseProviderID
   ,OrderQuestionResponseProviderNM
   ,OrderQuestionResponseProviderSpecialtyNM
   ,OrderQuestionResponseMedicationID
   ,OrderQuestionResponseMedicationNM
   ,OrderQuestionResponseTherapeuticClassCD
   ,OrderQuestionResponseTherapeuticClassNM
   ,OrderQuestionResponseDTS
   --,OrderQuestionTypeDSC
   ,OrderQuestionID
   --,OrderQuestionNM
   ,OrderQuestionResponseLineNBR
   ,OrderQuestionResponseTXT
FROM OrderQuestionResponse
WHERE OrderQuestionResponseSequenceNBR < 2 /* Remove duplicate medication orders. */
;

/****************************************************/
/* POPULATION EVENT - Suspected Infection Encounter */
/****************************************************/

/* All Patient Encounters with an Infection-Related Order-Question Response */

/* Grain: Primary patient encounter */

/* All Order-Question Responses Sequenced */
WITH OrderQuestionResponse AS (
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
   ,OrderQuestionResponseTXT
   ,OrderQuestionResponseDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PatientEncounterID ORDER BY OrderQuestionResponseDTS) AS InfectionSequenceNBR /* "1" indicates earliest infection */
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PatientEncounterID,OrderQuestionResponseTXT ORDER BY OrderQuestionResponseDTS) AS InfectionTypeSequenceNBR /* "1" indicates distinct infection type */
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventSuspectedInfection
)

/* Date of Earliest Infection-Related Order-Question Response per Encounter */
,FirstInfection AS (
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
   ,OrderQuestionResponseTXT AS FirstInfectionTXT
   ,OrderQuestionResponseDTS AS FirstInfectionDTS
FROM OrderQuestionResponse
WHERE InfectionSequenceNBR = 1
)

/* List of Distinct Infection-Related Order-Question Responses per Encounter */
,DistinctInfectionTypes AS (
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
   ,OrderQuestionResponseTXT AS DistinctInfectionTXT
   ,OrderQuestionResponseDTS AS DistinctInfectionDTS
FROM OrderQuestionResponse
WHERE InfectionTypeSequenceNBR = 1
)

/* All Infection-Related Order-Question Responses Concatenated in One Column */
,InfectionResponsesCombined AS (
SELECT
    i1.PatientEncounterID
   ,STUFF( /* STUFF removes leading semicolon. */
          (SELECT '; ' + CAST(DistinctInfectionTXT AS varchar(MAX))
           FROM DistinctInfectionTypes AS i2
         WHERE i2.PatientEncounterID = i1.PatientEncounterID /* Only combine infections per encounter. */
         ORDER BY DistinctInfectionDTS
         FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE /* Concatenate infections into XML first. */
        ).value('.','varchar(max)')
        ,1,1,'') AS InfectionCombinedDSC
FROM DistinctInfectionTypes AS i1
GROUP BY i1.PatientEncounterID
)

/* Concatenated Infection-Related Order-Question Responses and Date-Time of First One */
SELECT
     fi.PatientEncounterID
    ,irc.InfectionCombinedDSC
    ,fi.FirstInfectionDTS AS SuspectedInfectionDTS
    ,'Y' AS SuspectedInfectionFLG
    ,1 AS SuspectedInfectionFlagVAL
FROM FirstInfection AS fi
INNER JOIN InfectionResponsesCombined AS irc
   ON fi.PatientEncounterID = irc.PatientEncounterID
;

/************************/
/* POPULATION ENCOUNTER */
/************************/

/* The Population for this SAM Based on the Criteria in the Events and Rules Bindings with Added
   Demographic and Treatment Location Data */

/* Grain: Primary patient encounter */

/* Encounters for All Sepsis-Diagnosed, Suspected-Infection, or 2-SIRS Patients */
SELECT
    pca.PatientID
   ,pat.MRN
   ,pca.FacilityAccountID
   ,pca.PatientEncounterID
   ,peh.InpatientDataID  /* Used for joining to flowsheet data. */
   ,COALESCE(peh.ADTArrivalDTS,ha.AdmitDTS) AS AdmitDTS
   ,COALESCE(peh.HospitalDischargeDTS,ha.DischargeDTS) AS DischargeDTS
   ,COALESCE(ha.AdmitSourceDSC,'Unknown') AS AdmitSourceDSC
   ,COALESCE(peh.AdmitCategoryDSC,ha.AdmitCategoryDSC,'Unknown') AS AdmitCategoryDSC
   ,COALESCE(CAST(ha.AdmissionTypeCD AS VARCHAR(255)),'Unknown') AS AdmitTypeDSC
   --,fa.PrimaryServiceLineNM
   ,ha.PatientNM AS PatientFullNM
   ,ha.PatientGenderCD
   ,pat.EthnicGroupDSC AS PatientEthnicGroupDSC
   --,fa.RaceDSC AS PatientRaceDSC
   ,pat.BirthDTS
   ,(CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), ha.AdmitDTS, 112) AS INT) - CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), pat.BirthDTS, 112) AS INT)) / 10000.0 AS PatientAdmitAgeNBR
   --,fa.AdmitAgeNBR AS PatientAdmitAgeNBR
   --,fa.AdmitAgeGroupDSC AS PatientAdmitAgeGroupDSC
   ,pca.HospitalAccountClassCD
   ,pca.HospitalAccountClassDSC
   ,pca.DischargePhysicalLocationNM
   --,fa.DischargePhysicalDepartmentNM
   ,ha.DischargeDepartmentDSC AS DischargePhysicalDepartmentNM
   ,pca.DischargeDestinationCD
   ,pca.DischargeDestinationDSC
   ,pca.DischargeDispositionCD
   ,pca.DischargeDispositionDSC
   ,pca.PatientExpiredInHospitalFLG
   ,pca.PatientExpiredInHospitalFlagVAL
   --,fa.InpatientIndexAdmissionCNT /* Readmission denominator */
   --,COALESCE(CAST(fa.InpatientReadmit30FLG AS INT),0) AS InpatientReadmit30FlagVAL /* 30-day readmission flag */
   --,fa.TotalCostAMT
   --,fa.TotalVariableCostAMT
   --,fa.PrimaryPayorNM
   ,ha.FinancialClassDSC
   --,fa.CharlsonDeyoRiskScoreGroupingNBR
   --,fa.ElixhauserRiskScoreGroupingNBR
   --,fa.ElixhauserComorbidityDSC
   --,fa.CharlsonDeyoComorbidityDSC
   --,fa.APRDRG
   --,fa.APRDRGDSC
   --,fa.APRDRGSeverityWeightNBR
   --,fa.MSDRG
   --,fa.MSDRGDSC
   ,pca.PrimaryICDDiagnosisCD
   ,pca.PrimaryICDDiagnosisDSC
   ,pca.PrimaryICDDiagnosisCombinedCodeAndDSC
   ,pca.SecondaryICDDiagnosesCodesCombinedCD
   ,pca.SecondaryICDDiagnosesCombinedDSC
   ,pca.SecondaryICDDiagnosesCombinedCodeAndDSC
   ,pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG
   ,pca.SepsisDiagnosisFlagVAL
   ,pca.SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,pca.SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFlagVAL
   ,pca.SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,pca.SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFlagVAL
   ,pca.SepsisPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,pca.SepsisPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,pca.SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,pca.SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,pca.SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,pca.SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,pca.SuspectedInfectionAnd2SIRSDTS
   ,pca.SuspectedInfectionCombinedDSC
   ,pca.SuspectedInfectionDTS
   ,pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG
   ,pca.SuspectedInfectionFlagVAL
   ,pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG
   ,pca.SIRSCriteriaFlagVAL
   ,pca.SIRSFirstCriterionNM
   ,pca.SIRSFirstCriterionVAL
   ,pca.SIRSFirstCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,pca.SIRSFirstCriterionDTS
   ,pca.SIRSSecondCriterionNM
   ,pca.SIRSSecondCriterionVAL
   ,pca.SIRSSecondCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,pca.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS
   ,pca.SIRSTimeBetweenCriteriaMinsAMT
   ,pca.EDPatientFLG
   ,pca.EDPatientFlagVAL
   ,CASE
        WHEN pca.EDPatientFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SepsisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y' THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS EdSepsisPoaFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pca.EDPatientFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SepsisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y' THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS EdSepsisPoaFlagVAL
   ,CASE
        WHEN pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG = 'Y' THEN 1 /* Yes Sepsis Dx and Infection and 2 SIRS */
        WHEN pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG = 'N'
             AND pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG = 'Y' THEN 2 /* No Sepsis Dx, But Yes Infection and Yes 2 SIRS */
        WHEN pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG = 'N'
             AND pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG = 'N' THEN 3 /* Yes Sepsis Dx, But No Infection and No 2 SIRS */
    END AS DxOrInfectionSIRSCohortCD
   ,CASE
        WHEN pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG = 'Y' THEN 'Yes Sepsis Dx and Yes Infection and Yes 2 SIRS'
        WHEN pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG = 'N'
             AND pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG = 'Y' THEN 'No Sepsis Dx, But Yes Infection and Yes 2 SIRS'
        WHEN pca.SepsisDiagnosisFLG = 'Y'
             AND pca.SuspectedInfectionFLG = 'N'
             AND pca.SIRSCriteriaFLG = 'N' THEN 'Yes Sepsis Dx, But No Infection and No 2 SIRS'
    END AS DxOrInfectionSIRSCohortDSC
FROM SAM.Sepsis.RulePatientClassAndAge AS pca
/* When Shared.Clinical has data and is working, uncomment this join and its associated fields.
INNER JOIN Shared.Clinical.FacilityAccount AS fa
   ON pca.FacilityAccountID = fa.FacilityAccountID
*/
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Finance.HospitalAccount AS ha
   ON pca.PatientEncounterID = ha.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Encounter.PatientEncounterHospital AS peh
   ON pca.PatientEncounterID = peh.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Patient.Patient AS pat
   ON pca.PatientID = pat.PatientID
;

NOTE: If providers ask "How many SIRS criteria did my patient have?" this result set (destination entity) can be direct-queried for the answer: "One" or "Two" or (if the SIRSCriteriaFLG = "N" or if the patient is not in the result set at all) "None."

AttributeValues.AttributeValue:
/***********************************************************/
/* POPULATION RULE - Sepsis Diagnosis, SIRS, and Infection */
/***********************************************************/

/* All Sepsis-Diagnosed/At-Least-One-SIRS/Suspected-Infection Patient Encounters and Their ICD Diagnoses
   Rolled into One Row per Encounter */

/* Primary diagnoses are in one column; all others are concatenated in a secondary diagnoses column. */

/* Grain: Primary patient encounter */

/* NOTE: If providers ask "How many SIRS criteria did my patient have?" this result set (destination entity)
   can be direct-queried for the answer: "One" or "Two" or (if the SIRSCriteriaFLG = "N" or if the patient
   is not in the result set at all) "None." */

/* NOTE: Make sure an index has been added to Epic.Clinical.DiagnosisFacilityAccountICDBASE that includes
   FacilityAccountID, DiagnosisCD, DiagnosisDSC, LineNBR, and PresentOnAdmitDSC. If not, this binding may
   take significantly longer to run. */

/* All Primary Diagnoses per Encounter and a Flag for When Primary Diagnosis is Sepsis */
WITH PrimaryDiagnosis AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,AllDiagnosisCD AS PrimaryICDDiagnosisCD
   ,AllDiagnosisDSC AS PrimaryICDDiagnosisDSC
   ,AllDiagnosisCombinedDSC AS PrimaryICDDiagnosisCombinedCodeAndDSC
   ,CASE
        WHEN (DiagnosisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Yes'
	     OR DiagnosisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y')
         AND SepsisCodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN (DiagnosisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Yes'
	     OR DiagnosisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y')
         AND SepsisCodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL THEN 1
        ELSE 1
    END AS SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,CASE
        WHEN SepsisCodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN SepsisCodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFlagVAL
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis
WHERE PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'Y' /* Only the primary diagnosis */
)

/* All Secondary Diagnoses per Encounter Concatenated in One Column */
,SecondaryDiagnosis AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
    /* All Secondary ICD Codes */
   ,STUFF( /* STUFF removes leading semicolon. */
          (SELECT '; ' + AllDiagnosisCD
           FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis AS ad2
         WHERE ad2.FacilityAccountID = ad1.FacilityAccountID /* Only combine diagnoses per each encounter. */
           AND PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'N' /* Only secondary diagnoses */
         ORDER BY AllDiagnosisLineNBR
         FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE /* Concatenate diagnoses into XML first. */
        ).value('.','varchar(max)')
        ,1,1,'') AS SecondaryICDDiagnosesCodesCombinedCD
    /* All Secondary ICD Descriptions */
   ,STUFF( /* STUFF removes leading semicolon. */
          (SELECT '; ' + AllDiagnosisDSC
           FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis AS ad2
         WHERE ad2.FacilityAccountID = ad1.FacilityAccountID /* Only combine diagnoses per each encounter. */
           AND PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'N' /* Only secondary diagnoses */
         ORDER BY AllDiagnosisLineNBR
         FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE /* Concatenate diagnoses into XML first. */
        ).value('.','varchar(max)')
        ,1,1,'') AS SecondaryICDDiagnosesCombinedDSC
    /* All Secondary ICD Codes and Descriptions Combined */
   ,STUFF( /* STUFF removes leading semicolon. */
          (SELECT '; ' + AllDiagnosisCombinedDSC
           FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis AS ad2
         WHERE ad2.FacilityAccountID = ad1.FacilityAccountID /* Only combine diagnoses per each encounter. */
           AND PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'N' /* Only secondary diagnoses */
         ORDER BY AllDiagnosisLineNBR
         FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE /* Concatenate diagnoses into XML first. */
        ).value('.','varchar(max)')
        ,1,1,'') AS SecondaryICDDiagnosesCombinedCodeAndDSC
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis AS ad1
WHERE PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'N' /* Only secondary diagnoses */
GROUP BY FacilityAccountID,PatientEncounterID
)

/* Flagging Encounters with Secondary Diagnoses of Sepsis */
,SepsisSecondaryDiagnosis AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,'Y' AS SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,1 AS SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFlagVAL
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis
WHERE PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'N' /* Only secondary diagnoses */
  AND SepsisCodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL /* Only sepsis diagnoses */
GROUP BY
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
)

/* Flagging Encounters with Secondary Diagnoses of Sepsis Present on Admit (POA) */
,SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisPOA AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,'Y' AS SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,1 AS SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventAllDiagnosis
WHERE PrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'N' /* Only secondary diagnoses */
  AND SepsisCodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL /* Only sepsis diagnoses */
  AND DiagnosisPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Yes' /* Only diagnoses present on admit */
GROUP BY
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
)

/* All Primary and Secondary Diagnoses in One Row per Encounter with Sepsis Flags
   and All SIRS and Suspected Infection Information */
SELECT
    pd.FacilityAccountID
   ,pd.PatientEncounterID
   ,pd.PrimaryICDDiagnosisCD
   ,pd.PrimaryICDDiagnosisDSC
   ,pd.PrimaryICDDiagnosisCombinedCodeAndDSC
   ,sd.SecondaryICDDiagnosesCodesCombinedCD
   ,sd.SecondaryICDDiagnosesCombinedDSC
   ,sd.SecondaryICDDiagnosesCombinedCodeAndDSC
   ,CASE
        WHEN pd.SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'Y'
         OR ssd.SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFLG = 'Y' THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS SepsisDiagnosisFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pd.SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFLG = 'Y'
         OR ssd.SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFLG = 'Y' THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS SepsisDiagnosisFlagVAL
   ,pd.SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,pd.SepsisPrimaryDiagnosisFlagVAL
   ,COALESCE(ssd.SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFLG,'N') AS SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,COALESCE(ssd.SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFlagVAL,0) AS SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisFlagVAL
   ,CASE
        WHEN pd.SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y'
      OR ssdpoa.SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y' THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS SepsisPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pd.SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y'
      OR ssdpoa.SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG = 'Y' THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS SepsisPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,pd.SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,pd.SepsisPrimaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,COALESCE(ssdpoa.SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG,'N') AS SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,COALESCE(ssdpoa.SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL,0) AS SepsisSecondaryDxPresentOnAdmitFlagVAL
   ,CASE
        WHEN si.SuspectedInfectionDTS > sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS THEN si.SuspectedInfectionDTS
        WHEN si.SuspectedInfectionDTS < sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS THEN sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS
        ELSE NULL /* Return NULL when one or the other date-time is missing. */
    END AS SuspectedInfectionAnd2SIRSDTS
   ,si.InfectionCombinedDSC AS SuspectedInfectionCombinedDSC
   ,si.SuspectedInfectionDTS
   ,COALESCE(si.SuspectedInfectionFLG,'N') AS SuspectedInfectionFLG
   ,COALESCE(si.SuspectedInfectionFlagVAL,0) AS SuspectedInfectionFlagVAL
   ,sirs.SIRSFirstCriterionNM
   ,sirs.SIRSFirstCriterionVAL
   ,sirs.SIRSFirstCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,sirs.SIRSFirstCriterionDTS
   ,sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionNM
   ,sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionVAL
   ,sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,sirs.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS
   ,sirs.SIRSTimeBetweenCriteriaMinsAMT
   ,COALESCE(sirs.SIRSCriteriaFLG,'N') AS SIRSCriteriaFLG
   ,COALESCE(sirs.SIRSCriteriaFlagVAL,0) AS SIRSCriteriaFlagVAL
FROM PrimaryDiagnosis AS pd
INNER JOIN SecondaryDiagnosis AS sd
   ON pd.PatientEncounterID = sd.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SepsisSecondaryDiagnosis AS ssd
   ON pd.PatientEncounterID = ssd.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SepsisSecondaryDiagnosisPOA AS ssdpoa
   ON sd.PatientEncounterID = ssdpoa.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.EventSuspectedInfectionEncounter AS si
   ON pd.PatientEncounterID = si.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.EventSIRSCriterion AS sirs
   ON pd.PatientEncounterID = sirs.PatientEncounterID
;

/************************************/
/* POPULATION EVENT - All Diagnosis */
/************************************/

/* All ICD Diagnoses for Patients Diagnosed with Sepsis OR with Suspected Infection OR Who Met at Least One SIRS Criterion */

/* Grain: Diagnosis */


/* All Encounter IDs for Patients Diagnosed with Sepsis OR with Suspected Infection OR Who Met at Least One SIRS Criterion */
WITH Patients AS (
/* All Encounter IDs for Sepsis-Coded Patients */
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
FROM Epic.Finance.HospitalAccount AS ha
/* When Shared.Clinical has data and is working, use this join to replace the HospitalAccountDiagnosisBASE one below.
INNER JOIN Shared.Clinical.DiagnosisFacilityAccountICD AS dfa
   ON ha.HospitalAccountID = dfa.FacilityAccountID
*/
INNER JOIN Epic.Finance.HospitalAccountDiagnosisBASE AS dfa
   ON ha.HospitalAccountID = dfa.HospitalAccountID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryCode AS c /* Limit to sepsis-coded patients. */
   ON dfa.ReferenceBillCD = c.CodeValueTXT
  AND c.CodeTypeCD IN ('1' /* ICD9DX */
                      ,'2' /* ICD10DX */
                      )
  AND c.CodeGroupCD IN('1' /* Sepsis */
                      ,'2' /* Severe Sepsis */
                      ,'3' /* Septic Shock */
                      )
  AND c.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */

UNION ALL

/* All Encounter IDs for Infection Patients */
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventSuspectedInfectionEncounter AS sai

UNION ALL

/* All Encounter IDs for SIRS Patients */
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventSIRSCriterion
)

/* Distinct Encounter IDs for All of the Above Patients */
,DistinctPatients AS (
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
FROM Patients
GROUP BY PatientEncounterID
)

/* ICD Diagnoses, One per Row, for All of the Above Patients and Indications for Which Are Sepsis, Which Are Primary,
   Which Are Secondary, and Which Are present on admit. */
SELECT
    ha.PatientID
   ,ha.HospitalAccountID AS FacilityAccountID
   ,dp.PatientEncounterID
   ,ha.AdmitDTS
   ,ha.DischargeDTS
   ,c.CodeTypeNM AS SepsisCodeTypeNM
   ,c.CodeGroupNM AS SepsisCodeGroupNM
   ,dfa.LineNBR AS AllDiagnosisLineNBR
   ,COALESCE(dfa.ReferenceBillCD,'') AS AllDiagnosisCD /* Part of composite key. Can be blank but cannot NULL. */
   ,COALESCE(dfa.DiagnosisNM,'') AS AllDiagnosisDSC /* Part of composite key. Can be blank but cannot NULL. */
   ,UPPER(CONVERT(varchar,dfa.ReferenceBillCD)) + ' - ' + dfa.DiagnosisNM AS AllDiagnosisCombinedDSC
   ,dfa.DiagnosisPresentOnAdmitFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN dfa.LineNBR = '1' THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS PrimaryDiagnosisFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN c.CodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS SepsisDiagnosisFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN c.CodeGroupNM IS NOT NULL THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS SepsisDiagnosisFlagVAL
FROM DistinctPatients AS dp
INNER JOIN Epic.Finance.HospitalAccount AS ha
   ON dp.PatientEncounterID = ha.PatientEncounterID
/* When Shared.Clinical has data and is working, use this join to replace the HospitalAccountDiagnosisBASE one below.
LEFT OUTER JOIN Shared.Clinical.DiagnosisFacilityAccountICD AS dfa
   ON ha.HospitalAccountID = dfa.FacilityAccountID
*/
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Finance.HospitalAccountDiagnosisBASE AS dfa
   ON ha.HospitalAccountID = dfa.HospitalAccountID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryCode AS c /* Indicate where diagnoses are for sepsis, present on admit, etc. */
   ON dfa.ReferenceBillCD = c.CodeValueTXT
  AND c.CodeTypeCD IN ('1' /* ICD9DX */
                      ,'2' /* ICD10DX */
                      )
  AND c.CodeGroupCD IN('1' /* Sepsis */
                      ,'2' /* Severe Sepsis */
                      ,'3' /* Septic Shock */
                      )
  AND c.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
;

AttributeValues.AttributeValue:
/*************************************/
/* POPULATION EVENT - SIRS Criterion */
/*************************************/

/* All Encounters for Patients Who Have Met at Least One SIRS Criterion, Along with Their Respective SIRS
   Information and a Flag for Whether They Met One or Two SIRS Criteria */

/*
SIRS Criteria - At least the first two of the following:
    * Temperature < 36� C or > 38� C (< 96.8� F or > 100.4� F)
    * Heart Rate > 90 bpm
    * Respiratory Rate > 20 or pCO2 < 32 mmHg
    * (WBC Count > 12,000 or < 4,000) or > 10% band
*/

/* Grain: Primary encounter */

/* Respiratory Rate or pCO2 */
/* NOTE: Since this criterion calls for either respiratory rate > 20 or pCO2 < 32,
         these two measures need to be combined first, then sequenced. */
WITH Resp_pCO2 AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,FlowsheetItemDSC AS ComponentNM
   ,MeasureTXT AS ResultNBR
   ,' bpm' AS MeasureUnitDSC
   ,RecordedDTS AS ResultTimeDTS
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventVitalSignUnitConversion
WHERE FlowsheetItemCD = 4 /* Respiratory Rate */
  AND TRY_CAST(MeasureTXT as float) > 20

UNION ALL

SELECT
    ha.HospitalAccountID AS FacilityAccountID
   ,ha.PatientEncounterID AS PatientEncounterID
   ,c.ComponentNM
   ,TRY_CAST(lr.ResultTXT as float) AS ResultNBR
   ,' mmHg' AS MeasureUnitDSC
   ,lr.ResultTimeDTS
FROM Epic.Finance.HospitalAccount AS ha
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Result AS lr
   ON ha.PatientEncounterID = lr.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Reference.Component AS c
   ON lr.ComponentID = c.ComponentID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryLaboratory AS del
   ON lr.ComponentID = del.ComponentID
WHERE del.LabTypeCD = 3 /* Blood Gas */
  AND TRY_CAST(lr.ResultTXT as float) < 32
)

,AllMeasure AS (
/* Respiratory Rate and pCO2 - Combined and Sequenced */
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,ComponentNM
   ,ResultNBR
   ,MeasureUnitDSC
   ,ResultTimeDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PatientEncounterID ORDER BY ResultTimeDTS) AS MeasureSequenceNBR
FROM Resp_pCO2

UNION ALL

/* WBC Count or Bands */
SELECT
    ha.HospitalAccountID AS FacilityAccountID
   ,ha.PatientEncounterID
   ,c.ComponentNM
   ,TRY_CAST(lr.ResultTXT as float) AS ResultNBR
   ,CASE
        /*lr.ReferenceRangeUnitCD*/
	   WHEN del.LabTypeCD = 4 THEN ' K/uL'
        WHEN del.LabTypeCD = 5 THEN '%'
    END AS MeasureUnitDSC
   ,lr.ResultTimeDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY ha.PatientEncounterID ORDER BY lr.ResultTimeDTS) AS MeasureSequenceNBR
FROM Epic.Finance.HospitalAccount AS ha
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Result AS lr
   ON ha.PatientEncounterID = lr.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Reference.Component AS c
   ON lr.ComponentID = c.ComponentID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryLaboratory AS del
   ON lr.ComponentID = del.ComponentID
  AND del.LabTypeCD IN (4 /* White Blood Cell */
				   ,5 /* Band Cell */
				   )
WHERE ((del.LabTypeCD = 4 /* White Blood Cell */
  AND (TRY_CAST(lr.ResultTXT as float) > 12 OR TRY_CAST(lr.ResultTXT as float) < 4)
      )
   OR (del.LabTypeCD = 5 /* Band Cell */
  AND TRY_CAST(lr.ResultTXT as float) > 10)
      )

UNION ALL

/* Temperature */
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,FlowsheetItemDSC AS ComponentNM
   ,MeasureTXT AS ResultNBR
   ,'� F' AS MeasureUnitDSC
   ,RecordedDTS AS ResultTimeDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PatientEncounterID ORDER BY RecordedDTS) AS MeasureSequenceNBR
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventVitalSignUnitConversion
WHERE FlowsheetItemCD = 3 /* Temperature */
  AND (TRY_CAST(MeasureTXT as float) < 96.8
    OR TRY_CAST(MeasureTXT as float) > 100.4)  /* 36 C and 38 C */

UNION ALL

/* Pulse */
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,FlowsheetItemDSC AS ComponentNM
   ,MeasureTXT AS ResultNBR
   ,' bpm' AS MeasureUnitDSC
   ,RecordedDTS AS ResultTimeDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PatientEncounterID ORDER BY RecordedDTS) AS MeasureSequenceNBR
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventVitalSignUnitConversion
WHERE FlowsheetItemCD = 5 /* Pulse */
  AND TRY_CAST(MeasureTXT as float) > 90
)

/* Only First Values for Each Measure Type Sequenced */
,FirstMeasure AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,ComponentNM
   ,ResultNBR
   ,MeasureUnitDSC
   ,ResultTimeDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PatientEncounterID ORDER BY ResultTimeDTS,ComponentNM) AS FirstMeasureSequenceNBR
FROM AllMeasure
WHERE MeasureSequenceNBR = 1 /* First SIRS results for each measure type */
)

/* First SIRS Criterion */
,FirstCriterion AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,ComponentNM AS SIRSFirstCriterionNM
   ,ResultNBR AS SIRSFirstCriterionVAL
   ,CAST(ResultNBR as varchar(10)) + MeasureUnitDSC AS SIRSFirstCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,ResultTimeDTS AS SIRSFirstCriterionDTS
FROM FirstMeasure
WHERE FirstMeasureSequenceNBR = 1
)

/* Second SIRS Criterion */
,SecondCriterion AS (
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,ComponentNM AS SIRSSecondCriterionNM
   ,ResultNBR AS SIRSSecondCriterionVAL
   ,CAST(ResultNBR as varchar(10)) + MeasureUnitDSC AS SIRSSecondCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,ResultTimeDTS AS SIRSSecondCriterionDTS
FROM FirstMeasure
WHERE FirstMeasureSequenceNBR = 2
)

SELECT DISTINCT
    fm.FacilityAccountID
   ,fm.PatientEncounterID
   ,one.SIRSFirstCriterionNM
   ,one.SIRSFirstCriterionVAL
   ,one.SIRSFirstCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,one.SIRSFirstCriterionDTS
   ,two.SIRSSecondCriterionNM
   ,two.SIRSSecondCriterionVAL
   ,two.SIRSSecondCriterionAndUnitVAL
   ,two.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,one.SIRSFirstCriterionDTS,two.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS) AS SIRSTimeBetweenCriteriaMinsAMT
   ,CASE
        WHEN two.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS SIRSCriteriaFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN two.SIRSSecondCriterionDTS IS NOT NULL THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS SIRSCriteriaFlagVAL
FROM FirstMeasure AS fm
LEFT OUTER JOIN FirstCriterion AS one
   ON fm.PatientEncounterID = one.PatientEncounterID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SecondCriterion AS two
   ON fm.PatientEncounterID = two.PatientEncounterID
;

/*************************************************/
/* POPULATION EVENT - Vital Sign Unit Conversion */
/*************************************************/

/* All Vital Sign Measurements for All Patient Types--Plus Any Measurement Unit Conversions */

/* Grain: Vital signs (identical to that of SAM.Sepsis.EventVitalSign). */

/* Note: A common conversion is for patient body weight from ounces to kilograms. For more
   conversions, create and UNION a new SELECT statement for each one in similar fashion. */

/* Vital Measurements for All Patients Sequenced per Vital-Measurement Type */
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,FlowsheetItemCD
   ,FlowsheetItemDSC
   ,MeasureTXT
   ,RecordedDTS
   ,MeasureSequenceNBR
   ,EncounterMeasureSequenceNBR
   ,0 AS MeasureUnitConversionTypeCD
   ,'Not a Conversion' AS MeasureUnitConversionTypeDSC
   ,'N' AS MeasureUnitConversionFLG
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventVitalSign

UNION

/* Patient Body-Weight Conversion from Ounces to Kilograms */
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,FlowsheetItemCD
   ,'Weight-Kilograms' AS FlowsheetItemDSC
   ,CAST((TRY_CONVERT(float,MeasureTXT) * .0283495568397) as varchar(255)) AS MeasureTXT
   ,RecordedDTS
   ,MeasureSequenceNBR
   ,EncounterMeasureSequenceNBR
   ,1 AS MeasureUnitConversionTypeCD
   ,'Ounce to Kilogram' AS MeasureUnitConversionTypeDSC
   ,'Y' AS MeasureUnitConversionFLG
FROM SAM.Sepsis.EventVitalSign
WHERE FlowsheetItemCD = 6 /* Weight-Ounces */

/**************************/
/* PREMETRIC - Antibiotic */
/**************************/

/* Each Antibiotic Administration with Its Corresponding Order, Order-Acknowledgment, and Dispensation */

/* Grain: Medication administration */

/* Medication Data */
WITH Medications AS (
SELECT
/* Medications - Not Compounded */
    mref.MedicationID
   ,mref.MedicationDSC
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassCD
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassDSC
   ,'Not Compounded' AS CompoundedDSC
FROM Epic.Reference.Medication AS mref
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryMedication AS dem
   ON mref.MedicationID = dem.MedicationID
  AND dem.UsageCD = 1 /* Sepsis Antibiotics */
  AND dem.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */

UNION ALL

/* Medications - Compounded */
/* Note: This is included because some medications might only be captured as compounded medications. */
SELECT DISTINCT
    mref.MedicationID
   ,mref.MedicationDSC
   ,COALESCE(MixMed.TherapeuticClassCD,mref.TherapeuticClassCD) AS TherapeuticClassCD
   ,COALESCE(MixMed.TherapeuticClassDSC,mref.TherapeuticClassDSC) AS TherapeuticClassDSC
   ,'Compounded' AS CompoundedDSC
FROM Epic.Reference.Medication AS mref
INNER JOIN Epic.Pharmacy.MixtureComponent AS mix
   ON mref.MedicationID = mix.MedicationID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryMedication AS dem
   ON mref.MedicationID = dem.MedicationID
  AND dem.UsageCD = 1 /* Sepsis Antibiotics */
  AND dem.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
INNER JOIN Epic.Reference.Medication AS MixMed
   ON mix.DrugID = MixMed.MedicationID
WHERE(mref.TherapeuticClassCD IS NULL
   OR mref.PharmaceuticalClassCD IS NULL)
  AND MixMed.TherapeuticClassCD = dem.TherapeuticClassCD
  AND mix.ContactDateRealNBR IN (
                           SELECT
                               MAX(ContactDateRealNBR)
                           FROM Epic.Pharmacy.MixtureComponent
                           WHERE MedicationID = mix.MedicationID
                          )
)

/* Antibiotics - Order Data */
,AbxOrder AS (
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,ord.OrderID
   ,ord.OrderStatusDSC
   ,COALESCE(ord.OrderingProviderID,ord.MedicationPrescribingProviderID,ord.AuthorizingProviderID,'Unknown') AS AbxOrderProviderID
   ,COALESCE(OrdProv.ProviderFullNM,'Unknown') AS AbxOrderProviderNM
   ,COALESCE(OrdProv.PrimarySpecialtyNM,'Unknown') AS AbxOrderProviderSpecialtyNM
   ,mref.MedicationID AS AbxOrderMedicationID
   ,mref.MedicationDSC AS AbxOrderMedicationNM
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassCD AS AbxOrderTherapeuticClassCD
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassDSC AS AbxOrderTherapeuticClassNM
   ,mref.CompoundedDSC AS AbxCompoundedDSC
   ,ord.OrderInstantDTS AS AbxOrderDTS
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,tz.TimeZeroDTS,ord.OrderInstantDTS) AS TimeZeroToAbxOrderMinsAMT
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY pop.PatientEncounterID ORDER BY ord.OrderInstantDTS) AS OrderSequenceNBR
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Medication AS ord
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = ord.PatientEncounterID
INNER JOIN medications AS mref
   ON ord.MedicationID = mref.MedicationID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Shared.Person.Provider AS OrdProv
   ON COALESCE(ord.OrderingProviderID,ord.MedicationPrescribingProviderID,ord.AuthorizingProviderID) = OrdProv.EDWProviderID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.MetricTimeZero AS tz
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = tz.PatientEncounterID
)

/* Antibiotics - Order-Acknowledgement Data */
/*
,AbxAck AS (
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,ord.OrderID
   ,COALESCE(ack.AcknowledgeUserID,'Unknown') AS AbxAcknowledgeProviderID
   ,COALESCE(AckProv.UserNM,'Unknown') AS AbxAcknowledgeProviderNM
   ,ord.MedicationID AS AbxAcknowledgeMedicationID
   ,ord.MedicationDSC AS AbxAcknowledgeMedicationNM
   ,ack.AcknowledgeDTS AS AbxAcknowledgeDTS
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,tz.TimeZeroDTS,ack.AcknowledgeDTS) AS TimeZeroToAbxAcknowledgeMinsAMT
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY ack.OrderID ORDER BY ack.AcknowledgeDTS) AS AcknowledgeSequenceNBR
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN Epic.Clinical.AdministeredMedication AS mar
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = mar.MARCSNID
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Medication AS ord
   ON mar.OrderID = ord.OrderID
INNER JOIN medications AS mref
   ON ord.MedicationID = mref.MedicationID
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Acknowledge AS ack
   ON mar.OrderID = ack.OrderID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Person.Employee AS AckProv
   ON ack.AcknowledgeUserID = AckProv.UserID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.MetricTimeZero AS tz
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = tz.PatientEncounterID
)
*/

/* Antibiotics - Dispensation Data */
,AbxDispense AS (
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,ord.OrderID
   ,COALESCE(dis.PharmacyUserID,'Unknown') AS AbxDispenseProviderID
   ,COALESCE(DisProv.UserNM,'Unknown') AS AbxDispenseProviderNM
   ,dis.DispensePharmacyID AS AbxDispensePharmacyID
   ,pharm.PharmacyNM AS AbxDispensePharmacyNM
   ,ord.MedicationID AS AbxDispenseMedicationID
   ,ord.MedicationDSC AS AbxDispenseMedicationNM
   ,dis.ActionDTS AS AbxDispenseDTS
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,tz.TimeZeroDTS,dis.ActionDTS) AS TimeZeroToAbxDispenseMinsAMT
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY dis.OrderID ORDER BY dis.ActionDTS) AS DispenseSequenceNBR
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Medication AS ord
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = ord.PatientEncounterID
INNER JOIN medications AS mref
   ON ord.MedicationID = mref.MedicationID
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.DispenseBASE AS dis
   ON ord.OrderID = dis.OrderID
      AND dis.OrderContactTypeCD = 4 /* 'Verify' */
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Person.Employee AS DisProv
   ON dis.PharmacyUserID = DisProv.UserID
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Pharmacy.Pharmacy AS pharm
   ON dis.DispensePharmacyID = pharm.PharmacyID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.MetricTimeZero AS tz
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = tz.PatientEncounterID
)

/* Antibiotics - Administration Data */
,AbxAdmin AS (
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,mar.OrderID
   ,COALESCE(mar.UserID,'Unknown') AS AbxAdminProviderID
   ,COALESCE(AdminProv.UserNM,'Unknown') AS AbxAdminProviderNM
   ,mref.MedicationID AS AbxAdminMedicationID
   ,mref.MedicationDSC AS AbxAdminMedicationNM
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassCD AS AbxTherapeuticClassCD
   ,mref.TherapeuticClassDSC AS AbxTherapeuticClassNM
   ,mref.CompoundedDSC AS AbxCompoundedDSC
   ,mar.MedicationTakenDTS AS AbxAdministeredDTS
   ,mar.MARActionCD
   ,mar.MARActionDSC
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,tz.TimeZeroDTS,mar.MedicationTakenDTS) AS TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY mar.OrderID ORDER BY mar.MedicationTakenDTS) AS OrderAdminSequenceNBR /* The sequence of order-specific administrations */
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY pop.PatientEncounterID ORDER BY mar.MedicationTakenDTS) AS EncounterAdminSequenceNBR /* The sequence of encounter-specific administrations */
   ,tz.TimeZeroDTS AS AbxTimeZeroDTS
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN Epic.Clinical.AdministeredMedication AS mar
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = mar.MARCSNID
INNER JOIN Epic.Orders.Medication AS ord
   ON mar.OrderID = ord.OrderID
INNER JOIN Medications AS mref
   ON ord.MedicationID = mref.MedicationID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryMedicationRoute AS demr
   ON mar.RouteCD = demr.RouteCD
  AND demr.UsageCD = 1 /* Sepsis Antibiotics */
  AND demr.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryMedicationAdminstrationAction AS demaa
   ON mar.MARActionCD = demaa.AdministrationActionCD
  AND demaa.UsageCD = 1 /* Sepsis Antibiotics */
  AND demaa.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
LEFT OUTER JOIN Epic.Person.Employee AS AdminProv
   ON mar.UserID = AdminProv.UserID
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.MetricTimeZero AS tz
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = tz.PatientEncounterID
WHERE(ord.OrderStatusDSC <> 'Canceled'
   OR ord.OrderStatusDSC IS NOT NULL)
)

/* All ABX administrations and their corresponding (and preceding) orders, order-acknowledgments, and dispensations */
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,aa.OrderID
   ,ao.OrderStatusDSC
   ,aa.AbxTimeZeroDTS
    /* Orders */
   ,ao.AbxOrderMedicationID AS AbxFirstOrderMedicationID
   ,ao.AbxOrderMedicationNM AS AbxFirstOrderMedicationNM
   ,ao.AbxOrderTherapeuticClassCD
   ,ao.AbxOrderTherapeuticClassNM
   ,ao.AbxOrderProviderID
   ,ao.AbxOrderProviderNM
   ,ao.AbxOrderProviderSpecialtyNM
   ,aa.AbxCompoundedDSC
   ,ao.AbxOrderDTS
   ,ao.TimeZeroToAbxOrderMinsAMT
   ,ao.OrderSequenceNBR
    /* Acknowledgments */
/*
   ,ac.AbxAcknowledgeProviderID
   ,ac.AbxAcknowledgeProviderNM
   ,ac.AbxAcknowledgeDTS
   ,ac.TimeZeroToAbxAcknowledgeMinsAMT
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,ao.AbxOrderDTS,ac.AbxAcknowledgeDTS) AS AbxOrderToAcknowledgeMinsAMT
*/
    /* Dispensations */
   ,ad.AbxDispenseProviderID
   ,ad.AbxDispenseProviderNM
   ,ad.AbxDispensePharmacyNM
   ,ad.AbxDispenseDTS
   ,ad.TimeZeroToAbxDispenseMinsAMT
   --,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,ac.AbxAcknowledgeDTS,ad.AbxDispenseDTS) AS AbxAcknowledgeToDispenseMinsAMT
    /* Administrations */
   ,aa.AbxAdminMedicationID AS AbxFirstAdminMedicationID
   ,aa.AbxAdminMedicationNM AS AbxFirstAdminMedicationNM
   ,aa.MARActionCD
   ,aa.MARActionDSC
   ,aa.AbxAdminProviderID
   ,aa.AbxAdminProviderNM
   ,aa.AbxAdministeredDTS
   ,aa.TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT
   --,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,ac.AbxAcknowledgeDTS,aa.AbxAdministeredDTS) AS AbxAcknowledgeToAdminMinsAMT
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,ad.AbxDispenseDTS,aa.AbxAdministeredDTS) AS AbxDispenseToAdminMinsAMT
   ,DATEDIFF(MINUTE,ao.AbxOrderDTS,aa.AbxAdministeredDTS) AS AbxOrderToAdminMinsAMT
   ,COALESCE(aa.EncounterAdminSequenceNBR,'0') AS EncounterAdminSequenceNBR /* The sequence of encounter-specific administrations - May be used in composite key. Since can't be NULL, COALESCE to zero. */
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN AbxAdmin AS aa

/*********************/
/* METRIC - ED Event */
/*********************/

/* Each Earliest ED Event Type per Encounter */

/* Grain: Primary patient encounter */

/* All ED Events for the Population */
WITH EDEvent AS (
SELECT
    pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,e.EventDTS
   ,e.EventNM
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN Epic.Clinical.EDEvent AS e
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = e.PatientEncounterID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryDepartment AS ded
   ON e.DepartmentID = ded.DepartmentID
      AND ded.DepartmentTypeCD = 1 /* Emergency */
      AND ded.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryEDEvent AS deed
   ON e.EventNM = deed.EDEventNM
  AND deed.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
WHERE (e.EventStatusDSC <> 'Deleted'
    OR e.EventStatusDSC IS NULL)
)

/* Each Earliest ED Event, Pivoted to One Row per Encounter */
,EDEventPremetric AS (
SELECT
    PatientEncounterID
   ,[Patient arrived in ED] AS EdArrivalDTS
   ,[Registration Completed] AS EdRegistrationDTS
   ,[Triage Started] AS EdTriageStartDTS
   ,[Triage Completed] AS EdTriageCompletedDTS
   ,[Comprehensive Triage Complete] AS EdComprehensiveTriageCompleteDTS
   ,[Assign Nurse] AS EdNurseAssignedDTS
   ,[Assign Attending] AS EdAttendingAssignedDTS
   ,[Assign Midlevel or Attending] AS EdMidlevelOrAttendingAssignedDTS
   ,[Assign Midlevel] AS EdMidlevelAssignedDTS
   ,[Team Member Assigned] AS EdTeamMemberAssignedDTS
   ,[ED Chart Analysis] AS EdChartAnalysisDTS
   ,[Patient roomed in ED] AS EdRoomDTS
   ,[Nursing Assessment Complete] AS EdNursingAssessmentCompleteDTS
   ,[Patient Ready for Admit] AS EdPatientReadyForAdmitDTS
   ,[Patient admitted] AS EdPatientAdmittedFromEdDTS
   ,[Admitted] AS EdAdmittedFromEdDTS
   ,[Patient transferred] AS EdPatientTransferredDTS
   ,[Patient transferred to OTF] AS EdPatientTransferredToOtfDTS
   ,[Patient discharged] AS EdDischargDTS
   ,[Patient departed from ED] AS EdDepartDTS
FROM EDEvent PIVOT(MIN(EventDTS) FOR EventNM IN(
    [Patient arrived in ED]
   ,[Registration Completed]
   ,[Triage Started]
   ,[Triage Completed]
   ,[Comprehensive Triage Complete]
   ,[Assign Nurse]
   ,[Assign Attending]
   ,[Assign Midlevel or Attending]
   ,[Assign Midlevel]
   ,[Team Member Assigned]
   ,[ED Chart Analysis]
   ,[Patient roomed in ED]
   ,[Nursing Assessment Complete]
   ,[Patient Ready for Admit]
   ,[Patient admitted]
   ,[Admitted]
   ,[Patient transferred]
   ,[Patient transferred to OTF]
   ,[Patient discharged]
   ,[Patient departed from ED])) AS PV
)

/* Each Earliest ED Event Type and Final (Exit) ED Event per Encounter */
SELECT
    eep.PatientEncounterID
   ,CASE
        WHEN eep.EdArrivalDTS IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS EdAdmitFLG
   ,eep.EdArrivalDTS
   ,eep.EdRegistrationDTS
   ,eep.EdTriageStartDTS
   ,COALESCE(eep.EdTriageCompletedDTS,eep.EdComprehensiveTriageCompleteDTS) AS EdTriageCompletedDTS
   ,eep.EdNurseAssignedDTS
   ,eep.EdAttendingAssignedDTS
   ,eep.EdMidlevelOrAttendingAssignedDTS
   ,eep.EdMidlevelAssignedDTS
   ,eep.EdTeamMemberAssignedDTS
   ,eep.EdChartAnalysisDTS
   ,eep.EdRoomDTS
   ,eep.EdNursingAssessmentCompleteDTS
   ,eep.EdPatientReadyForAdmitDTS
   ,COALESCE(eep.EdPatientAdmittedFromEdDTS,eep.EdAdmittedFromEdDTS) AS EdPatientAdmittedFromEdDTS
   ,COALESCE(eep.EdPatientTransferredDTS,eep.EdPatientTransferredToOtfDTS) AS EdPatientTransferredDTS
   ,eep.EdDischargDTS
   ,eep.EdDepartDTS
   ,pee.EdExitEventNM /* The last ED event per encounter */
   ,pee.EdExitEventDTS /* The date and time of the last ED event per encounter */
FROM EDEventPremetric AS eep
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.MetricEDExit AS pee
   ON eep.PatientEncounterID = pee.PatientEncounterID
;

/********************/
/* METRIC - ED Exit */
/********************/

/* The Final ED Event per Encounter, Defined as the Exit Event, with Its Date and Time */

/* Grain: Primary patient encounter */

/* All Potential ED Exit Events Sequenced */
WITH EDExit AS (
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,e.EventNM
   ,e.EventDTS
   ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY pop.PatientEncounterID ORDER BY e.EventDTS DESC) AS EventSequenceNBR
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN Epic.Clinical.EDEvent AS e
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = e.PatientEncounterID
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.DataEntryEDEvent AS deed
   ON e.EventTypeCD = deed.EDEventCD
  AND deed.EDEventTypeCD = 1 /* ED Exit Event */
  AND deed.DataEntryEntityItemStatusCD = 1 /* Active */
WHERE e.PatientEncounterID IS NOT NULL
  AND (e.EventStatusDSC <> 'Deleted'
    OR e.EventStatusDSC IS NULL)
)

/* The Final ED Event per Encounter and Its Timestamp */
SELECT
    FacilityAccountID
   ,PatientEncounterID
   ,EventNM AS EdExitEventNM
   ,EventDTS AS EdExitEventDTS
FROM EDExit
WHERE EventSequenceNBR = 1 /* Final ED event per encounter */
;

/***********************/
/* METRIC - Antibiotic */
/***********************/

/* First Antibiotic Administrations and Their Corresponding Orders, Order-acknowledgments, and Dispensations */

/* Also creates 3-hour-bundle-compliance flags. */

/* Grain: Primary patient encounter */

/* Only First Administrations from the Premetric Binding */
SELECT
    pop.FacilityAccountID
   ,pop.PatientEncounterID
   ,pa.OrderID
   ,pa.AbxCompoundedDSC
   ,pa.AbxTimeZeroDTS
    /* Orders */
   ,pa.AbxFirstOrderMedicationID
   ,pa.AbxFirstOrderMedicationNM
   ,pa.AbxOrderProviderID AS AbxFirstOrderProviderID
   ,pa.AbxOrderProviderNM AS AbxFirstOrderProviderNM
   ,pa.AbxOrderProviderSpecialtyNM AS AbxFirstOrderProviderSpecialtyNM
   ,pa.AbxOrderDTS AS AbxFirstOrderDTS
   ,pa.TimeZeroToAbxOrderMinsAMT
    /* Acknowledgments */
/*
   ,pa.AbxAcknowledgeProviderID AS AbxFirstAcknowledgeProviderID
   ,pa.AbxAcknowledgeProviderNM AS AbxFirstAcknowledgeProviderNM
   ,pa.AbxAcknowledgeDTS AS AbxFirstAcknowledgeDTS
   ,pa.TimeZeroToAbxAcknowledgeMinsAMT
   ,pa.AbxOrderToAcknowledgeMinsAMT
*/
    /* Dispensations */
   ,pa.AbxDispenseProviderID AS AbxFirstDispenseProviderID
   ,pa.AbxDispenseProviderNM AS AbxFirstDispenseProviderNM
   ,pa.AbxDispensePharmacyNM AS AbxFirstDispensePharmacyNM
   ,pa.AbxDispenseDTS AS AbxFirstDispenseDTS
   ,pa.TimeZeroToAbxDispenseMinsAMT
--   ,pa.AbxAcknowledgeToDispenseMinsAMT
    /* Administrations */
   ,pa.AbxFirstAdminMedicationID
   ,pa.AbxFirstAdminMedicationNM
   ,pa.AbxAdminProviderID AS AbxFirstAdminProviderID
   ,pa.AbxAdminProviderNM AS AbxFirstAdminProviderNM
   ,pa.AbxAdministeredDTS AS AbxFirstAdminDTS
   ,pa.TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT
--   ,pa.AbxAcknowledgeToAdminMinsAMT
   ,pa.AbxDispenseToAdminMinsAMT
   ,pa.AbxOrderToAdminMinsAMT
    /* Compliance */
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAdministeredDTS IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS AbxPresentFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT <= 180 THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS AbxComplianceFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT <= 180 THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS AbxComplianceFlagVAL
    /* New York State DOH Measure - Administration Within 1 Hour */
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT <= 60 THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS AbxAdminWithinOneHourFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.TimeZeroToAbxAdminMinsAMT <= 60 THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS AbxAdminWithinOneHourFlagVAL
    /* Activity Sequence - Flags to Filter Patient Encounters Whose ABX Orders Are
       Administered Before They Are Acknowledged or Before They Are Dispensed */
/*
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAcknowledgeDTS <= pa.AbxAdministeredDTS THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS AbxAcknowledgeBeforeAdminFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAcknowledgeDTS <= pa.AbxAdministeredDTS THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS AbxAcknowledgeBeforeAdminFlagVAL
*/
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxDispenseDTS <= pa.AbxAdministeredDTS THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS AbxDispenseBeforeAdminFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxDispenseDTS <= pa.AbxAdministeredDTS THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS AbxDispenseBeforeAdminFlagVAL
    /* Flag for ABX Administration Prior to Last ED Exit Event */
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAdministeredDTS < ee.EdExitEventDTS THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS ReceivedAbxInEdFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAdministeredDTS < ee.EdExitEventDTS THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS ReceivedAbxInEdFlagVAL
    /* Flag for Use as Summary Metric Indicating Any Abx Administration */
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAdministeredDTS IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
        ELSE 'N'
    END AS ReceivedAbxFLG
   ,CASE
        WHEN pa.AbxAdministeredDTS IS NOT NULL THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS ReceivedAbxFlagVAL
FROM SAM.Sepsis.PopulationEncounter AS pop
INNER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.PremetricAntibiotic AS pa
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = pa.PatientEncounterID
      AND pa.EncounterAdminSequenceNBR = 1
LEFT OUTER JOIN SAM.Sepsis.MetricEDExit AS ee
   ON pop.PatientEncounterID = ee.PatientEncounterID
;
